The Art of the Matrix


HQ PDF | 488 pages 

The Art of The Matrix goes beyond the film. But you cannot be told what this book isÃ¢â‚¬Â¦you have to see it for yourself! First published in February 2001, almost two years after the release of the now landmark film (March 31, 1999), this almost 500-page (including gatefolds), five pound, one-of-a-kind book with over 1,000 color and black-and-white illustrations, is the pre-production archive of the script, artwork, and conceptual drawings. Over 26,000 copies have been sold to date and acclaimed by reviewers and fans of The Matrix worldwide.
